FBIS4-60643 "drnes103_j_94012" FBIS-NES-94-103 Daily Report 26 May 1994 ARABIAN PENINSULA Yemen Salih Receives Cables on Unity Anniversary Salih Receives Cables on Unity Anniversary JN2605183994 Sanaa Yemeni Republic Radio Network in Arabic 1700 GMT 26 May 94 JN2605183994 Sanaa Yemeni Republic Radio Network Arabic BFN [Text] Lieutenant General 'Ali 'Abdallah Salih, Presidential Council chairman, has received a cable of congratulations on the fourth anniversary of the Republic of Yemen's National Day from South Africa's President Nelson Mandela. The president sent a cable of thanks in reply. The brother Presidential Council chairman also received two cables of congratulations on the fourth anniversary of the Republic of Yemen's National Day from Iranian President 'Ali Akbar Hashemi-Rafsanjani and Eritrean President Issaias Afeworke. The brother Presidential Council chairman sent cables of thanks in reply.
